    "title": "Account Setup",
    "description": "Configure your SearchFit account to get the most out of the platform.",
    "content": "After creating your account, follow these steps to configure SearchFit for your needs.\n\n## Creating Your Account\n\n1. Visit the [sign up page](/auth/sign-up)\n2. Enter your email and create a password, or sign in with Google\n3. Verify your email address\n4. Complete your profile setup\n\n## Adding Your First Domain\n\nOnce logged in, add your primary domain:\n\n1. Navigate to **Dashboard** → **Domains**\n2. Click **Add Domain**\n3. Enter your domain name\n4. Optionally verify ownership for additional features\n\n### Domain Verification\n\nVerifying domain ownership unlocks:\n- Historical tracking data\n- Automated monitoring\n- Integration with Search Console\n- Priority support\n\nVerification methods:\n- **DNS Record** - Add a TXT record to your DNS\n- **HTML File** - Upload a verification file to your site\n- **Meta Tag** - Add a meta tag to your homepage\n\n## Configuring Notifications\n\nStay informed about your AI visibility:\n\n1. Go to **Settings** → **Notifications**\n2. Choose your notification preferences:\n   - Email alerts for score changes\n   - Weekly summary reports\n   - Competitor movement alerts\n   - New recommendation notifications\n\n## Team Access\n\nInvite team members to collaborate:\n\n1. Navigate to **Settings** → **Team**\n2. Click **Invite Member**\n3. Enter their email and select a role:\n   - **Admin** - Full access to all features\n   - **Editor** - Can run reports and make changes\n   - **Viewer** - Read-only access to reports\n\n## Billing Setup\n\nManage your subscription:\n\n1. Go to **Settings** → **Billing**\n2. View your current plan and usage\n3. Upgrade or modify your subscription\n4. Update payment methods\n\n## Next Steps\n\n<div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\">\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/docs/integrations\">\n    <h3>Connect Integrations</h3>\n    <p>Link your existing tools</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/docs/ai-tracking\">\n    <h3>AI Tracking</h3>\n    <p>Start monitoring your AI visibility</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n</div>",
