    "title": "AEO Reports",
    "description": "Understanding your AI Engine Optimization report and metrics.",
    "content": "The AEO (Answer Engine Optimization) Report is SearchFit's flagship analysis that measures how well your brand performs across AI platforms.\n\n## What's in an AEO Report?\n\nYour report includes comprehensive analysis across multiple dimensions:\n\n### Overall AEO Score\n\nA score from 0-100 representing your overall AI visibility:\n\n| Score Range | Rating | Description |\n|-------------|--------|-------------|\n| 80-100 | Excellent | Strong AI presence, frequently recommended |\n| 60-79 | Good | Solid visibility with room for improvement |\n| 40-59 | Fair | Moderate presence, significant opportunities |\n| 20-39 | Poor | Limited AI visibility |\n| 0-19 | Critical | Minimal or no AI presence |\n\n### Platform Breakdown\n\nIndividual scores for each AI platform:\n\n- **ChatGPT Score** - Performance in OpenAI's assistant\n- **Perplexity Score** - Visibility in AI search\n- **Claude Score** - Presence in Anthropic's assistant\n- **Gemini Score** - Performance in Google's AI\n\n## Report Sections\n\n### Brand Awareness\n\nMeasures whether AI platforms know about your brand:\n\n- **Recognition Rate** - How often AI recognizes your brand name\n- **Information Accuracy** - Whether AI has correct information\n- **Entity Definition** - How well AI understands what you do\n\n### Recommendation Score\n\nHow likely AI is to recommend your brand:\n\n- **Direct Recommendations** - When users ask for solutions\n- **List Inclusions** - Appearing in \"best of\" lists\n- **Comparison Mentions** - Being mentioned alongside competitors\n\n### Content Citation\n\nWhether AI platforms cite your content:\n\n- **Citation Frequency** - How often your content is referenced\n- **Source Authority** - How your site is perceived as a source\n- **Topic Coverage** - Topics where you're cited\n\n### Competitive Position\n\nHow you compare to competitors:\n\n- **Market Position** - Where you rank vs competitors\n- **Share of Voice** - Percentage of mentions in your category\n- **Competitive Gaps** - Where competitors outperform you\n\n## Recommendations\n\nEach report includes prioritized recommendations:\n\n### High Impact\nActions that will significantly improve your score:\n- Fix critical accuracy issues\n- Add missing structured data\n- Create FAQ content for common queries\n\n### Medium Impact\nImprovements that will incrementally boost visibility:\n- Enhance about page content\n- Improve entity clarity\n- Build authoritative backlinks\n\n### Low Impact\nNice-to-have improvements:\n- Minor content updates\n- Additional schema markup\n- Social profile optimization\n\n## Understanding Metrics\n\n### Mention Sentiment\n\nHow AI platforms discuss your brand:\n\n- **Positive** - Favorable mentions, recommendations\n- **Neutral** - Factual mentions without judgment\n- **Negative** - Critical mentions, complaints\n- **Mixed** - Combination of sentiments\n\n### Accuracy Assessment\n\nWhether AI information is correct:\n\n- **Correct** - Information matches reality\n- **Outdated** - Information was once correct\n- **Incorrect** - Factually wrong information\n- **Unknown** - Unable to verify\n\n### Coverage Score\n\nHow comprehensively AI covers your brand:\n\n- Services/products mentioned\n- Locations covered\n- Team members recognized\n- History and background\n\n## Report Comparisons\n\n### Historical Comparison\n\nCompare your current report to previous reports:\n\n1. Go to **Reports** → **History**\n2. Select two reports to compare\n3. View score changes and trends\n4. Identify improvements and regressions\n\n### Competitor Comparison\n\nCompare your report to competitors:\n\n1. Add competitor domains\n2. Generate reports for each\n3. View side-by-side comparison\n4. Identify competitive advantages\n\n## Scheduling Reports\n\nSet up automatic report generation:\n\n1. Go to **Reports** → **Schedule**\n2. Choose frequency (weekly, monthly)\n3. Select domains to include\n4. Configure delivery method\n5. Add recipients for email delivery\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Generate regularly** - Track progress over time\n2. **Act on recommendations** - Implement suggested changes\n3. **Monitor competitors** - Stay aware of market changes\n4. **Share with stakeholders** - Keep team informed\n5. **Celebrate wins** - Acknowledge improvements",
