      "raw": "AI Tracking is SearchFit's core feature that monitors how AI platforms perceive and recommend your brand.\n\n## How AI Tracking Works\n\nSearchFit queries AI platforms with questions relevant to your industry and monitors:\n\n- **Mention Frequency** - How often your brand is mentioned\n- **Mention Context** - Whether mentions are positive, neutral, or need improvement\n- **Accuracy** - Whether AI platforms have correct information about your business\n- **Ranking** - Where you appear in AI-generated lists and recommendations\n\n## Supported Platforms\n\n### ChatGPT (OpenAI)\n\nThe most widely used AI assistant. We track:\n- Brand mentions in conversational responses\n- Accuracy of business information\n- Recommendation patterns\n\n### Perplexity\n\nAn AI-powered search engine gaining significant market share. We monitor:\n- Appearance in search results\n- Citation of your content\n- Answer box inclusions\n\n### Claude (Anthropic)\n\nA thoughtful AI assistant known for accuracy. We track:\n- Brand awareness and perception\n- Factual accuracy of mentions\n- Competitive positioning\n\n### Gemini (Google)\n\nGoogle's AI platform with deep integration into search. We monitor:\n- AI Overview appearances\n- Brand entity recognition\n- Local business mentions\n\n## Setting Up Tracking\n\n### Automatic Tracking\n\nOnce you add a domain to SearchFit, basic tracking begins automatically:\n\n1. Daily queries about your brand\n2. Weekly comprehensive analysis\n3. Monthly trend reports\n\n### Custom Queries\n\nConfigure specific queries to track:\n\n1. Go to **AI Tracking** → **Custom Queries**\n2. Click **Add Query**\n3. Enter the question you want to monitor\n4. Select which platforms to track\n5. Set tracking frequency\n\nExample queries:\n- \"What are the best [your industry] companies?\"\n- \"Who provides [your service] in [your location]?\"\n- \"What is [your brand name]?\"\n\n## Understanding Your Metrics\n\n### Visibility Score\n\nA composite score (0-100) based on:\n- Mention frequency across platforms\n- Mention quality and context\n- Accuracy of information\n- Competitive ranking\n\n### Platform Scores\n\nIndividual scores for each AI platform, helping you identify where to focus optimization efforts.\n\n### Trend Analysis\n\nTrack your visibility over time:\n- Daily snapshots\n- Weekly summaries\n- Month-over-month comparisons\n- Year-over-year trends\n\n## Alerts and Notifications\n\nConfigure alerts for:\n\n- **Score Changes** - Get notified when your visibility score changes significantly\n- **New Mentions** - Alerts when AI platforms start mentioning your brand\n- **Accuracy Issues** - Notifications when AI provides incorrect information\n- **Competitor Movement** - Alerts when competitors gain or lose visibility\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Track consistently** - Set up regular monitoring schedules\n2. **Monitor competitors** - Add competitor domains for comparison\n3. **Act on insights** - Use recommendations to improve visibility\n4. **Verify accuracy** - Regularly check that AI has correct business info",
