    "title": "Analytics",
    "description": "AI-powered insights and performance metrics for your visibility.",
    "content": "SearchFit Analytics provides comprehensive insights into your performance across both traditional search and AI platforms.\n\n## Dashboard Overview\n\nYour analytics dashboard shows:\n\n- **Overall Visibility Score** - Combined SEO + AEO performance\n- **Platform Breakdown** - Performance by platform\n- **Trend Charts** - Historical performance data\n- **Quick Insights** - AI-generated recommendations\n\n## Key Metrics\n\n### Visibility Metrics\n\n| Metric | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| AEO Score | Your AI visibility rating (0-100) |\n| Mention Count | Total mentions across AI platforms |\n| Sentiment Score | Positive/neutral/negative analysis |\n| Accuracy Rate | How often AI information is correct |\n\n### SEO Metrics\n\n| Metric | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| Organic Traffic | Search engine visitors |\n| Keyword Rankings | Position tracking |\n| Backlink Count | Total referring domains |\n| Domain Authority | Overall domain strength |\n\n### Combined Insights\n\nSearchFit correlates SEO and AEO data to provide unique insights:\n\n- How SEO improvements affect AI visibility\n- Which content performs best across both channels\n- Where to focus optimization efforts\n\n## Custom Reports\n\nCreate custom reports for your needs:\n\n1. Go to **Analytics** → **Custom Reports**\n2. Click **Create Report**\n3. Select metrics to include\n4. Choose date range and comparison periods\n5. Save and schedule\n\n### Report Types\n\n- **Executive Summary** - High-level overview for stakeholders\n- **Technical Deep Dive** - Detailed metrics for SEO teams\n- **Competitor Analysis** - Side-by-side comparisons\n- **Content Performance** - Content-specific analytics\n\n## Data Sources\n\nSearchFit combines data from:\n\n### Native Data\n- AI platform monitoring\n- Content analysis\n- Technical audits\n\n### Connected Integrations\n- Google Analytics\n- Google Search Console\n- Social media platforms\n- CRM systems\n\n## Exporting Data\n\nExport your analytics in multiple formats:\n\n- **PDF Reports** - Formatted for sharing\n- **CSV Export** - Raw data for analysis\n- **API Access** - Programmatic data retrieval\n- **Scheduled Emails** - Automatic report delivery\n\n## Insights Engine\n\nOur AI-powered insights engine automatically:\n\n- Identifies trends and anomalies\n- Suggests optimization opportunities\n- Predicts future performance\n- Prioritizes action items\n\n### Insight Categories\n\n- **Opportunities** - Areas for improvement\n- **Alerts** - Issues requiring attention\n- **Wins** - Recent positive changes\n- **Predictions** - Forecasted trends\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Review weekly** - Check analytics at least weekly\n2. **Set benchmarks** - Establish baseline metrics\n3. **Track trends** - Focus on directional changes, not daily fluctuations\n4. **Act on insights** - Use recommendations to drive improvements",
