    "title": "Backlinks",
    "description": "Monitor and analyze your backlink profile for better visibility.",
    "content": "Backlinks remain a crucial ranking factor for both SEO and increasingly for AI visibility. SearchFit helps you monitor and improve your backlink profile.\n\n## Why Backlinks Matter for AEO\n\nAI platforms consider authority signals when deciding which sources to cite and recommend. A strong backlink profile:\n\n- Establishes your site as authoritative\n- Increases likelihood of AI citations\n- Improves trust signals across platforms\n- Supports overall visibility scores\n\n## Backlink Dashboard\n\nYour backlink dashboard shows:\n\n- **Total Backlinks** - All links pointing to your site\n- **Referring Domains** - Unique domains linking to you\n- **Domain Rating** - Overall link authority score\n- **New vs Lost** - Link acquisition and loss tracking\n\n## Monitoring Features\n\n### New Backlink Alerts\n\nGet notified when you earn new links:\n\n1. Go to **Backlinks** → **Settings**\n2. Enable **New Link Alerts**\n3. Set minimum domain authority threshold\n4. Choose notification method\n\n### Lost Backlink Tracking\n\nMonitor when links disappear:\n\n- Automatic detection of removed links\n- Context about why links may have been removed\n- Suggestions for link reclamation\n\n### Competitor Backlink Analysis\n\nSee where competitors get their links:\n\n1. Add competitor domains\n2. View their backlink profile\n3. Identify link opportunities\n4. Find common linking patterns\n\n## Link Quality Assessment\n\nNot all backlinks are equal. SearchFit evaluates:\n\n### Authority Metrics\n- Domain Rating (DR)\n- Page Authority\n- Trust Flow\n\n### Relevance Signals\n- Topical relevance\n- Geographic relevance\n- Industry alignment\n\n### Risk Indicators\n- Spam score\n- Link farm detection\n- Potential penalties\n\n## Backlink Opportunities\n\nSearchFit identifies link building opportunities:\n\n### Unlinked Mentions\nFinds sites mentioning your brand without linking.\n\n### Competitor Gap Analysis\nIdentifies sites linking to competitors but not you.\n\n### Broken Link Opportunities\nFinds relevant broken links you could replace.\n\n### Resource Page Prospects\nIdentifies resource pages in your niche.\n\n## Link Building Outreach\n\nManage outreach campaigns:\n\n1. Go to **Backlinks** → **Outreach**\n2. View identified opportunities\n3. Generate personalized outreach templates\n4. Track email status and responses\n5. Mark links as acquired\n\n## Disavow Management\n\nHandle toxic backlinks:\n\n1. Review flagged links in **Backlinks** → **Toxic**\n2. Investigate potentially harmful links\n3. Add to disavow list if needed\n4. Export disavow file for Search Console\n\n## Reports\n\nGenerate backlink reports:\n\n- **Profile Overview** - Complete backlink summary\n- **New Links Report** - Recent acquisitions\n- **Competitor Comparison** - Side-by-side analysis\n- **Opportunity Report** - Link building prospects\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Quality over quantity** - Focus on authoritative, relevant links\n2. **Monitor regularly** - Check for new and lost links weekly\n3. **Analyze competitors** - Learn from their link strategies\n4. **Diversify sources** - Build links from varied domains\n5. **Track ROI** - Measure impact on visibility scores",
