    "title": "Content",
    "description": "Generate SEO and AEO-optimized content with AI assistance.",
    "content": "SearchFit's Content feature helps you create content that ranks well in both traditional search engines and AI-powered platforms.\n\n## AI-Powered Content Generation\n\nOur content tools leverage AI to help you create:\n\n- **Blog posts** optimized for search and AI visibility\n- **Product descriptions** that convert\n- **Landing pages** designed for discovery\n- **FAQ content** structured for AI answer engines\n\n## Getting Started with Content\n\n### Content Templates\n\nChoose from pre-built templates:\n\n1. Go to **Content** → **Create New**\n2. Select a template type:\n   - Blog Post\n   - Product Page\n   - Landing Page\n   - FAQ Section\n   - Comparison Article\n3. Enter your topic and keywords\n4. Generate and refine\n\n### Custom Content\n\nFor more control:\n\n1. Select **Custom Content**\n2. Describe what you want to create\n3. Specify tone, length, and style\n4. Add keywords to target\n5. Generate and edit\n\n## AEO-Optimized Content\n\nContent optimized for Answer Engine Optimization includes:\n\n### Structured Data\n\nAutomatically generates:\n- FAQ schema markup\n- HowTo structured data\n- Product schema\n- Organization data\n\n### Question-Based Sections\n\nFormats content to answer common questions, making it easier for AI to extract and cite.\n\n### Entity Optimization\n\nEnsures your content:\n- Clearly identifies your brand entity\n- Links to authoritative sources\n- Establishes topical authority\n\n## Content Analysis\n\nBefore publishing, analyze your content:\n\n### Readability Score\nEnsures content is accessible and easy to understand.\n\n### Keyword Coverage\nVerifies target keywords are naturally included.\n\n### AEO Score\nPredicts how well the content will perform with AI platforms.\n\n### Competitor Comparison\nSee how your content stacks up against competitors.\n\n## Content Calendar\n\nPlan and schedule your content:\n\n1. Navigate to **Content** → **Calendar**\n2. View upcoming content\n3. Drag and drop to reschedule\n4. Set publishing reminders\n\n## Integration with CMS\n\nPublish directly to your CMS:\n\n- **WordPress** - Direct publishing and updating\n- **Webflow** - Export formatted content\n- **Shopify** - Product and blog content\n- **Custom CMS** - API integration available\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Start with research** - Use AI Tracking insights to identify content gaps\n2. **Focus on questions** - Structure content around user questions\n3. **Update regularly** - Keep content fresh for both SEO and AEO\n4. **Measure results** - Track how content affects your visibility scores",
