    "title": "Free Report",
    "description": "Get a free AI visibility report for any domain.",
    "content": "SearchFit offers a free AEO report for any domain, giving you instant insights into your AI visibility without creating an account.\n\n## Getting Your Free Report\n\n### Step 1: Enter Your Domain\n\nVisit [SearchFit's homepage](/) and enter your domain in the search field.\n\n<Callout>\nNo need to include `https://` or `www.` - just enter `yourdomain.com`\n</Callout>\n\n### Step 2: Wait for Analysis\n\nOur system will:\n- Query AI platforms about your domain\n- Analyze responses and mentions\n- Calculate your AEO score\n- Generate recommendations\n\nThis typically takes 30-60 seconds.\n\n### Step 3: View Results\n\nYour free report includes:\n- Overall AEO score\n- Platform breakdown (ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, Gemini)\n- Top recommendations\n- Competitor snapshot\n\n## What's Included\n\n### Free Report Features\n\n| Feature | Included |\n|---------|----------|\n| Overall AEO Score | Yes |\n| Platform Breakdown | Yes |\n| Top 5 Recommendations | Yes |\n| Basic Competitor View | Yes |\n| Detailed Analysis | Limited |\n| Historical Tracking | No |\n| PDF Download | Requires email |\n| Custom Reports | No |\n\n### Upgrading for More\n\nCreate a free account to access:\n- Full detailed analysis\n- Historical report tracking\n- Unlimited reports\n- Dashboard access\n\nPaid plans add:\n- Advanced analytics\n- Competitor monitoring\n- Content tools\n- Integrations\n- API access\n\n## PDF Download\n\nTo download a PDF of your free report:\n\n1. Complete your report generation\n2. Click **Download PDF**\n3. Enter your email address\n4. Verify the reCAPTCHA\n5. Receive download link via email\n\n### Why Email Required?\n\nWe request your email to:\n- Deliver the PDF link securely\n- Notify you when the PDF is ready\n- Provide follow-up tips (optional)\n\n<Callout>\nWe respect your privacy. Unsubscribe from tips anytime, and we never share your email.\n</Callout>\n\n## Understanding Your Score\n\n### Score Interpretation\n\n| Score | What It Means |\n|-------|---------------|\n| 80+ | Excellent AI visibility - you're well-positioned |\n| 60-79 | Good visibility with clear improvement areas |\n| 40-59 | Moderate visibility - significant opportunity |\n| 20-39 | Low visibility - action needed |\n| 0-19 | Minimal AI presence - critical attention required |\n\n### Platform Scores\n\nEach platform score indicates:\n- How well that AI knows your brand\n- Whether information is accurate\n- Likelihood of recommendations\n\n## Free Report Limitations\n\nThe free report provides a snapshot but has limitations:\n\n### Not Included\n- Full mention analysis\n- Historical comparisons\n- Detailed competitor data\n- Custom recommendations\n- Ongoing monitoring\n- API access\n\n### Report Expiration\n- Free reports are available for 7 days\n- After 7 days, regenerate for fresh data\n- Create an account to save reports permanently\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### How often can I generate free reports?\n\nYou can generate a free report once per domain per 24 hours.\n\n### Is my data saved?\n\nFree reports are stored temporarily (7 days) and then deleted. Create an account to save reports permanently.\n\n### Can I share my free report?\n\nYes! Use the share button to copy a link. The link expires when the report does.\n\n### Is the free report accurate?\n\nYes, free reports use the same analysis engine as paid reports. The difference is in the depth of detail provided.\n\n### Do I need to verify my domain?\n\nNo, domain verification is not required for free reports. Verification is optional for account holders who want additional features.\n\n## Next Steps\n\nAfter viewing your free report:\n\n<div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\">\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/auth/sign-up\">\n    <h3>Create Free Account</h3>\n    <p>Save reports and track progress over time</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/pricing\">\n    <h3>View Pricing</h3>\n    <p>Explore plans for advanced features</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n</div>\n\n## Getting Help\n\nNeed assistance with your free report?\n\n- **Documentation** - Browse our docs for guidance\n- **Contact** - Reach out via our [contact page](/contact)\n- **Community** - Join discussions (coming soon)",
