      "raw": "SearchFit is the comprehensive platform for tracking and optimizing your visibility across traditional search engines and AI-powered platforms like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, and Gemini.\n\n## What is SearchFit?\n\nIn the age of AI, users are increasingly discovering businesses through conversational AI assistants rather than traditional search engines. SearchFit helps you:\n\n- **Track AI Visibility** - Monitor how often and how accurately AI platforms mention your brand\n- **Optimize for AEO** - Implement Answer Engine Optimization strategies to improve your AI presence\n- **Generate Content** - Create SEO and AEO-optimized content with AI assistance\n- **Analyze Performance** - Get actionable insights from comprehensive analytics\n\n## Key Features\n\n### AI Tracking\nMonitor your brand's visibility across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, and Gemini. Understand how AI platforms perceive and recommend your business.\n\n### Content Generation\nCreate optimized content that ranks well in both traditional search and AI-powered answer engines.\n\n### Analytics Dashboard\nComprehensive analytics to track your progress, identify opportunities, and measure ROI.\n\n### Technical Audits\nAutomated SEO audits to identify and fix technical issues affecting your visibility.\n\n### Integrations\nConnect with 40+ tools including Google Analytics, Search Console, and popular CMS platforms.\n\n## Getting Started\n\nReady to improve your AI visibility? Here's how to get started:\n\n1. **[Create an account](/auth/sign-up)** - Sign up for free to explore the platform\n2. **[Run your first report](/docs/quick-start)** - Generate an AEO report for your domain\n3. **[Connect integrations](/docs/integrations)** - Link your existing analytics tools\n4. **[Explore the dashboard](/docs/account-setup)** - Navigate the features and start optimizing\n\n## Why AEO Matters\n\nTraditional SEO focuses on ranking in search engine results pages (SERPs). But with the rise of AI assistants, a new discipline has emerged: **Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)**.\n\nAEO ensures your business is accurately represented when AI systems answer user queries. This includes:\n\n- Being mentioned as a solution to user problems\n- Having accurate business information in AI responses\n- Being recommended in relevant contexts\n- Appearing in AI-generated comparisons and lists\n\nSearchFit provides the tools and insights you need to succeed in both SEO and AEO.",
