    "content": "SearchFit generates professional PDF reports that you can download, share with stakeholders, and use for presentations.\n\n## Generating a PDF Report\n\n### From Dashboard\n\n1. Navigate to any report in your dashboard\n2. Click the **Download PDF** button\n3. Wait for PDF generation (usually 10-30 seconds)\n4. Download starts automatically\n\n### From Report Page\n\n1. View your full AEO report\n2. Click **Export** → **Download PDF**\n3. Select sections to include (optional)\n4. Generate and download\n\n## PDF Contents\n\nYour PDF report includes:\n\n### Cover Page\n- Report title and date\n- Domain analyzed\n- Overall AEO score\n- SearchFit branding\n\n### Executive Summary\n- Key findings overview\n- Score breakdown by platform\n- Top 3 recommendations\n- Comparison to previous report\n\n### Detailed Analysis\n- Platform-by-platform breakdown\n- Mention analysis\n- Sentiment overview\n- Accuracy assessment\n\n### Recommendations\n- Prioritized action items\n- Impact assessment\n- Implementation guidance\n- Resource requirements\n\n### Appendix\n- Raw data tables\n- Methodology explanation\n- Glossary of terms\n\n## Customizing PDFs\n\n### Branding Options\n\nFor Pro and Enterprise plans:\n\n1. Go to **Settings** → **Branding**\n2. Upload your logo\n3. Set brand colors\n4. Choose header/footer text\n5. Save branding preferences\n\n### Section Selection\n\nChoose which sections to include:\n\n- Toggle sections on/off before generating\n- Reorder sections as needed\n- Add custom notes or context\n- Include or exclude competitor data\n\n## Sharing Reports\n\n### Direct Download\n\nDownload and share manually via:\n- Email attachment\n- Cloud storage (Google Drive, Dropbox)\n- Team messaging (Slack, Teams)\n\n### Shareable Link\n\nCreate a shareable link:\n\n1. Generate your PDF report\n2. Click **Share** → **Create Link**\n3. Set expiration (optional)\n4. Add password protection (optional)\n5. Copy and share the link\n\n### Scheduled Delivery\n\nAutomatically send reports:\n\n1. Go to **Reports** → **Schedule**\n2. Enable PDF delivery\n3. Add recipient email addresses\n4. Set delivery frequency\n5. Customize email message\n\n## Report History\n\nAccess previously generated PDFs:\n\n1. Go to **Reports** → **History**\n2. View all generated reports\n3. Re-download any past report\n4. Compare reports over time\n\n## File Specifications\n\n| Property | Value |\n|----------|-------|\n| Format | PDF 1.7 |\n| Page Size | A4 (default) or Letter |\n| Resolution | 300 DPI for images |\n| File Size | Typically 1-5 MB |\n| Accessibility | Tagged PDF, screen reader compatible |\n\n## Enterprise Features\n\nEnterprise plans include:\n\n### White Label Reports\n- Remove SearchFit branding\n- Add your company logo and colors\n- Custom report templates\n\n### Bulk Generation\n- Generate reports for multiple domains\n- Batch PDF creation\n- Bulk download or delivery\n\n### API Access\nGenerate PDFs programmatically:\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.searchfit.com/v1/reports/pdf \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"reportId\": \"abc123\"}'\n```\n\n### Custom Templates\nWork with our team to create:\n- Custom report layouts\n- Additional sections\n- Specialized analysis\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n### PDF Won't Generate\n\nIf PDF generation fails:\n\n1. Check your internet connection\n2. Ensure the report has completed\n3. Try a different browser\n4. Clear browser cache\n5. Contact support if issues persist\n\n### PDF Looks Wrong\n\nIf formatting is off:\n\n1. Use latest browser version\n2. Download fresh copy\n3. Check PDF viewer settings\n4. Report issue with screenshot\n\n### Download Issues\n\nIf download doesn't start:\n\n1. Check browser download settings\n2. Disable ad blockers temporarily\n3. Try right-click → Save As\n4. Use a different browser\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Generate fresh PDFs** - Always download current data\n2. **Use branding** - Customize for professional presentation\n3. **Include context** - Add notes for recipients\n4. **Schedule delivery** - Automate regular reporting\n5. **Archive important reports** - Save historical copies",
