    "title": "Quick Start",
    "description": "Get up and running with SearchFit in under 5 minutes.",
    "content": "This guide walks you through generating your first AI visibility report and understanding the results.\n\n## Step 1: Enter Your Domain\n\nFrom the homepage or dashboard, enter your website domain (e.g., `example.com`) in the search field.\n\n<Callout>\nYou don't need to include `https://` or `www.` - just the domain name is enough.\n</Callout>\n\n## Step 2: Generate Your Report\n\nClick **\"Get Free Report\"** to start the analysis. SearchFit will:\n\n1. Query multiple AI platforms about your domain\n2. Analyze how your brand is perceived\n3. Compile recommendations for improvement\n4. Generate a comprehensive AEO score\n\nThis process typically takes 30-60 seconds.\n\n## Step 3: Review Your Results\n\nYour AEO report includes several key sections:\n\n### Overall Score\nA score from 0-100 indicating your current AI visibility. Higher scores mean better representation across AI platforms.\n\n### AI Platform Breakdown\nSee how you perform on each platform:\n- **ChatGPT** - OpenAI's conversational AI\n- **Perplexity** - AI-powered search engine\n- **Claude** - Anthropic's AI assistant\n- **Gemini** - Google's AI platform\n\n### Recommendations\nActionable suggestions to improve your AI visibility, prioritized by impact.\n\n### Competitor Analysis\nSee how you compare to competitors in your industry.\n\n## Step 4: Take Action\n\nBased on your report, you can:\n\n- **Download PDF** - Share the report with your team\n- **Create Account** - Save reports and track progress over time\n- **Implement Fixes** - Follow the recommendations to improve your score\n\n## Next Steps\n\n<div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\">\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/docs/account-setup\">\n    <h3>Account Setup</h3>\n    <p>Configure your account and preferences</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n  <LinkedCard href=\"/docs/aeo-reports\">\n    <h3>Understanding Reports</h3>\n    <p>Deep dive into AEO report metrics</p>\n  </LinkedCard>\n</div>",
