    "content": "Social Listening helps you track what people are saying about your brand across social media platforms and the broader web, providing insights that complement your AI visibility data.\n\n## Why Social Listening Matters\n\nBrand mentions across social and web platforms:\n\n- Influence AI training data\n- Affect brand perception in AI responses\n- Provide early warning of reputation issues\n- Identify customer feedback and trends\n\n## Setting Up Monitoring\n\n### Brand Keywords\n\nConfigure keywords to track:\n\n1. Go to **Social Listening** → **Keywords**\n2. Add your brand name and variations\n3. Include common misspellings\n4. Add product names\n5. Include executive names (optional)\n\n### Platforms Monitored\n\nSearchFit monitors:\n\n- **X (Twitter)** - Real-time brand mentions\n- **LinkedIn** - Professional discussions\n- **Reddit** - Community conversations\n- **News Sites** - Media coverage\n- **Blogs** - Industry publications\n- **Forums** - Niche communities\n\n## Dashboard Overview\n\nYour social listening dashboard shows:\n\n- **Mention Volume** - Total mentions over time\n- **Sentiment Analysis** - Positive/neutral/negative breakdown\n- **Top Sources** - Where mentions originate\n- **Trending Topics** - Associated themes\n- **Influencer Activity** - High-profile mentions\n\n## Sentiment Analysis\n\nAutomatic sentiment classification:\n\n### Positive\nPraise, recommendations, success stories\n\n### Neutral\nGeneral mentions, news coverage, informational\n\n### Negative\nComplaints, criticism, issues\n\n### Alerts\nConfigure alerts for sentiment shifts or spikes in negative mentions.\n\n## Engagement Tools\n\nRespond to mentions directly:\n\n1. View mention in dashboard\n2. Click **View Source** to see original\n3. Use **Quick Reply** templates\n4. Track engagement history\n\n## Competitive Monitoring\n\nTrack competitor mentions:\n\n1. Add competitor brands to monitoring\n2. Compare mention volume\n3. Analyze sentiment differences\n4. Identify market trends\n\n## Influencer Identification\n\nFind people talking about your industry:\n\n- **Reach Score** - Audience size\n- **Engagement Rate** - Interaction levels\n- **Relevance** - Topic alignment\n- **Sentiment** - How they discuss your brand\n\n## Reports\n\nGenerate social listening reports:\n\n### Daily Digest\nQuick summary of previous day's activity\n\n### Weekly Summary\nTrends and highlights from the week\n\n### Monthly Analysis\nIn-depth analysis with recommendations\n\n### Custom Reports\nBuild reports for specific needs\n\n## Integration with AI Tracking\n\nSocial listening data enhances AI visibility insights:\n\n- Correlate social sentiment with AI mentions\n- Track how viral content affects AI perception\n- Identify topics that drive AI recommendations\n\n## Alert Configuration\n\nSet up custom alerts:\n\n| Alert Type | Trigger |\n|------------|---------|\n| Volume Spike | Unusual increase in mentions |\n| Sentiment Shift | Sudden change in sentiment |\n| Influencer Mention | High-profile account mentions you |\n| Competitor Alert | Competitor mentioned with your brand |\n| Keyword Match | Specific phrase detected |\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Monitor daily** - Check your dashboard regularly\n2. **Respond quickly** - Address negative mentions promptly\n3. **Track trends** - Look for patterns over time\n4. **Engage positively** - Build relationships with advocates\n5. **Learn from feedback** - Use insights to improve",
